<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Novo Episódio: <%= anime.titulo %></title>
    <style> 
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; } 
        .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #151515; color: #f9f9f9; } 
        .header { background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center; } 
        .header img { max-width: 180px; } 
        .content { padding: 30px; } 
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #E50914; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; } 
        .footer { background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5; } 
        h1, p { margin: 0 0 20px 0; } 
        h1 { font-size: 24px; color: #ffffff; } 
        p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; } 
        .episode-details { background-color: #242424; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-left: 3px solid #E50914; } 
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #0A0A0A;">
    <center>
        <table class="container" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #151515; color: #f9f9f9;">
            <tr>
                <td class="header" style="background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
                    <a href="<%= baseUrl || process.env.APP_URL || 'https://deny-animes-hub.onrender.com' %>" target="_blank">
                        <img src="<%= baseUrl || process.env.APP_URL || 'https://deny-animes-hub.onrender.com' %>/images/logo.png" alt="DenyAnimeHub Logo" style="max-width: 180px;">
                    </a>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <img src="<%= anime.imagemCapa || anime.imagemUrl %>" alt="Capa de <%= anime.titulo %>" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; height: auto; display: block;">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="content" style="padding: 30px;">
                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <h1 style="font-size: 24px; color: #ffffff; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Novo Episódio Disponível!</h1>
                                <div class="episode-details" style="background-color: #242424; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-left: 3px solid #E50914;">
                                    <h2 style="font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff; margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><%= anime.titulo %></h2>
                                    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #c5c5c5; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">Temporada <%= episodio.temporada || 1 %> • Episódio <%= episodio.numero %></p>
                                    <% if (episodio.titulo) { %>
                                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #c5c5c5; margin: 0;"><em>"<%= episodio.titulo %>"</em></p>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td align="center">
                                <a href="<%= urlDestino %>" target="_blank" class="button" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #E50914; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">Assistir Agora</a>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="footer" style="background-color: #0A0A0A; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5;">Você está recebendo este e-mail porque se inscreveu para receber notificações no DenyAnimeHub.</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #c5c5c5;">
                        <a href="<%= baseUrl || process.env.APP_URL || 'https://deny-animes-hub.onrender.com' %>/editar-perfil" target="_blank" style="color: #c5c5c5; text-decoration: underline;">Gerenciar Preferências</a> | 
                        © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> DenyAnimeHub
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>
</html>